  "detailed_description": "<h1>See our other games</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Face different challenges to help the little witch escape from a dungeon full of traps and enemies, where she was trapped by a great evil sorcerer. <br>Together with her bat friend, the little witch will have to jump, use her dash, she will face enemies that attack when they see her, evil witches who throw spells at her, she will have to jump over wooden thorns, sharp blades and saws, she will find puddles of acids on your way and logic challenges with keys and gates.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Walk<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167040/extras/73bed6efc3d21a078cbb6d3041315694.poster.avif?t=1688222792\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167040/extras/73bed6efc3d21a078cbb6d3041315694.webm?t=1688222792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167040/extras/73bed6efc3d21a078cbb6d3041315694.mp4?t=1688222792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Jump<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167040/extras/5a311c16524f2d965ab1002d55cfe07f.poster.avif?t=1688222792\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167040/extras/5a311c16524f2d965ab1002d55cfe07f.webm?t=1688222792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167040/extras/5a311c16524f2d965ab1002d55cfe07f.mp4?t=1688222792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Double Jump<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted l